>>   commit msg.
>> Patch 6:
>> - Asserted pixel_rst[i] reset in the loop after the err_disable_pixclk
>>   label.
>> - Modified Code Style for getting sys_rst and p_rst.
>> - Renamed clk_name to name and modified the relevant code.
